					<h5 class="heading">Export Readiness Assessment</h5>

					<p class="info">
						We conduct a thorough assessment of your business to determine its
						readiness for export. Our team evaluates factors such as product
						suitability, market demand, competitive advantage, production
						capacity, and regulatory compliance. Based on the assessment, we
						provide recommendations and develop a customized export strategy
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<div class="wrap">
					<h5 class="heading">Market Research and Analysis</h5>

					<p class="info">
						Understanding the target market is crucial for successful
						international expansion. We conduct in-depth market research and
						analysis to identify market trends, consumer preferences,
						competitive landscapes, and entry barriers. Our insights help
						businesses develop targeted marketing strategies and tailor their
						products or services to meet the needs of international customers
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<div class="wrap">
					<h5 class="heading">Export Promotion and Trade Missions</h5>

					<p class="info">
						Participation in trade missions and export promotion events can
						significantly boost business visibility and generate export
						opportunities. We organize trade missions, exhibitions, and business
						delegations to targeted markets, connecting businesses with
						potential buyers and partners. Our team assists in showcasing your
						products or services, networking, and exploring business
						collaborations
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<div class="wrap">
					<h5 class="heading">Legal Advisory and Compliance</h5>

					<p class="info">
						Navigating Nigeria's legal landscape requires expert guidance. Our
						team of legal experts provides comprehensive legal advisory and
						compliance services, covering contract drafting and review, dispute
						resolution, intellectual property protection, corporate governance,
						and regulatory compliance. We ensure businesses operate within legal
						frameworks, mitigating risks and ensuring legal compliance
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<div class="wrap">
					<h5 class="heading">Project Management</h5>

					<p class="info">
						Managing complex projects in Nigeria requires meticulous planning
						and execution. We offer project management services, overseeing
						project implementation, coordinating resources, managing timelines,
						and ensuring deliverables are met. Our experienced project managers
						ensure projects are executed efficiently, on time, and within budget
